---
title: Double American Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Onion Chutney & Mayo
description: Chicken and veggies, it’s a staple go-to for any dinner. Tonight we're going to mix it up! Cooking the chicken in our All-American spice blend gives it an additional burst of flavour, and an onion chutney glaze adds an irresistible sticky sweetness. Serve it alongside your favourite roast veg and you’ve got a new healthy chicken dinner!

